      "title": "MODELS & USAGE",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## TryOff Preprocess \u2014 Clothing Transfer\n\n**Models Required:**\n- \ud83d\udce5 [cat-tryoff-flux](https://huggingface.co/xiaozaa/cat-tryoff-flux) \u2192 models/cat-tryoff-flux/\n- \ud83d\udce5 [FLUX.1-dev](https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-dev) \u2192 models/checkpoints/FLUX.1-dev/\n- \ud83d\udce5 [SegFormer B2 Clothes](https://huggingface.co/mattmdjaga/segformer_b2_clothes) \u2192 models/segformer_b2_clothes/\n\n**Custom Nodes:** ComfyUI-Flux-TryOff, ComfyUI_LayerStyle, ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite\n\n**Flow (3 stages):**\n1. **Segmentation** \u2014 LoadImage (ref photo) \u2192 SegformerB2ClothesUltra \u2192 clothing mask\n2. **Processing** \u2014 LoadImage (ref photo) + mask \u2192 TryOffRunNode \u2192 garment_image & tryoff_image\n3. **Composition** \u2014 ImageCompositeMasked blends processed clothing back onto original photo\n\n**Output:** `reference_processed_*.png` \u2014 full person composite.\nLoad into scail2-animation.json LoadImage for SCAIL-2 REPLACE mode.\n\n**Preview:** Left = standalone garment (tryoff_image). Right = full person composite.\n\n**\u26a0\ufe0f VRAM:** CatVTON-Flux + FLUX.1-dev ~20GB (8-bit). Rode este workflow SOZINHO.\nFeche/recarregue o ComfyUI antes do workflow 2.\n\n**Params:** num_steps=20, guidance_scale=12 (TryOffLegacy v1.1 defaults)."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
